{"tid":1264641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]破壞公物會唔會有不合作運動嘅效果","createTime":"2019-06-28T19:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T20:59:56.000Z","uid":145377,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24e93ca919295b65ae0b8b4fd9d23bc3f8f3fe7c","tid":1264641,"uid":145377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"雖然不合作運動唔犯法,而破壞公物係犯法,同埋好難爭取民意,不過大範圍咁破壞公物一樣會好大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,例如周街拆燈柱,可能會搞到交通癱瘓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,又要政府動員同花費資金去修補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。想知咁樣會唔會有不合作運動嘅效果?仲會有咩其他後果?歡迎學術討論。<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔鼓吹犯法,想討論下社會唔同情況會有咩發生。"},{"pid":"92e289420509b730cb895a1bf90ce969cbfb6898","tid":1264641,"uid":145377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:13:16.000Z","msg":"推 發夢做任何野之前都要掌握個夢"},{"pid":"ada12c118675cbfa1f5f775a45e36ed04bb5017f","tid":1264641,"uid":145377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:24:32.000Z","msg":"(組隊拆撚左佢）香港CCTV燈柱計劃率先係九龍灣/觀塘/啟德安裝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1264264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1264264</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"96df7cdea4833af8fee4a9a8cba58eb5b9832f3a","tid":1264641,"uid":145377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:25:39.000Z","msg":"發夢見到如果有人拆可能要做好文宣"},{"pid":"77afcf0a59e5535e16acb96982b8f3aafc637c49","tid":1264641,"uid":145377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"Btw 甘地嘅不合作運動都有犯法,例如唔交稅唔上法庭"},{"pid":"1004a33a12ff3dd1d81a76bb9ee9eb224a889c95","tid":1264641,"uid":145377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:43:46.000Z","msg":"再推 點先可以啱香港人心意 可能好多香港人連發夢拆野都覺得暴力<br />\n<br />\n利申:反教條主義 唔覺得非暴力係天條 同埋唔覺得拆野好暴力"},{"pid":"119a751001ba6df9f0e2692cbe8797c2e247a4e4","tid":1264641,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28